      "title": "A unit to restructure public enterprises",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe said that a unit will be established for the restructuring of the government-owned business and 200 million rupees will be allocated for it."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
